rows.label: qev085405_MSG0001
rows.name: Hey, are you sure about this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0002
rows.name:
Yeah, I can trigger the door remotely
from my comm device once she's inside.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0003
rows.name:
So what, we just stand around and wait
until she decides to waltz in?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0004
rows.name: Er, I'm afraid so. Sorry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0005
rows.name: It's fine. Standing by is an important element of some missions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0006
rows.name:
She sure is taking her sweet time.
You'd think she'd be starving by now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0007
rows.name: Um, sir?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0008
rows.name: Hm?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0009
rows.name: Have you ever owned a pet before?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0010
rows.name: Yeah, a dog back on Earth. Why?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0011
rows.name:
I could tell from your face when you
suggested luring Aisha with food.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0012
rows.name: Heh. Yeah, that dog was an idiot for food.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0013
rows.name: Quiet![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0015
rows.name: Well, that sure as hell ain't Aisha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0018
rows.name: Oh no![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0019
rows.name: Aisha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0020
rows.name: Oh hell. She's gonna fight it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0021
rows.name: Dude, seriously?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0022
rows.name: Aisha, you idiot![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0023
rows.name: You're the idiot here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0024
rows.name: Huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0025
rows.name: We'll handle this. You and Aisha get back to NLA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085405_MSG0026
rows.name: Y-yes, sir![ST:wait ]
